# .gitignore

```gitignore
# Virtual Environment
.venv/
venv/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Environment Variables
.env

# VS Code
.vscode/

# PyCharm
.idea/

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Windows
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log

# Coverage
.coverage
htmlcov/

# Distribution
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
```
